Jeff Beck released this live album on 10 November 2008. Other performers
were Jason Rebello on keyboards, Vinnie Colaiuta on drums and
Tal Wilkenfeld on bass. The version of "A Day in the Life" featured on
this album was awarded a Grammy for Best Instrumental Rock performance.
The version of "Scatterbrain" also featured on this album was placed in
the hardest setlist, "Fjord of Swords", of the music video game
"Guitar Hero 5".
